i></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oic1665702717312.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oic1665702717312.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oic1665702717312.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oic1665702717312\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"oic1665702717312__message_leveldescriptions_from_where_and_order_by_clauses_491532\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">These messages show which <code class=\"ph codeph\">where</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">order</code> by clauses\n      are generated by Uniface. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oic1665702717312__p_d151976e1_d151977e1_d151978e1\">The information is formatted as follows:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oic1665702717312__p_d151979e1_d151980e1_d151981e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">where -&gt; field:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Fieldname</var> = <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">order by -&gt;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Fieldname</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ascending|descending</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oic1665702717312__p_d151982e1_d151983e1_d151984e1\">Each <code class=\"ph codeph\">where</code> clause appears on a separate line. The clauses are logically joined as AND constructions.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530592\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530592\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Message Level 16: Descriptions From where and order by Clauses Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 17, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 These messages show which where and order by clauses are generated by Uniface. The information is formatted as follows: where -> field: Fieldname = Value order by -> Fieldname ascending|descending Each where clause appears on a separate line. The clauses are logically joined as AND constructions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}